Class Candidate

java.lang.Object
Candidate
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Candidate>
public class Candidate
extends Object
implements Comparable<Candidate>
The purpose of this class is to create and represent a candidate using their name, affiliation, and number of votes casted for them
